    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "Your letter of January 20th has been received.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "In response to your inquiry, the FBI has not conducted",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "an investigation as you mentioned inasmuch as this would not come",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "within our investigative jurisdiction. The presence of an Agent was",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "simply to determine whether or not any violation may have occurred",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "in which the FBI would have an interest, and for no other reason.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "While I would like to be of assistance to you, the files",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "of the FBI must be maintained as confidential in accordance with",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "regulations of the Department of Justice and are available for official",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "use only. In view of this, I am sure you will understand why I cannot",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "be of any further assistance in this instance.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "status": "blank"
    },
